675f634ff132d4b47f2c1281.Description: The 9x19mm Hornady Critical Defense FTx® ammunition is a popular choice for self-defense. The patented FTX® bullet design ensures reliable expansion and penetration. Manufactured by Hornady.

templates.Name: 9x19mm Federal HST
templates.Description: The 9x19mm Federal HST ammunition is a popular choice for self-defense. The HST bullet design ensures reliable expansion and penetration, while the nickel-plated cases provide reliable feeding and corrosion resistance. Manufactured by Federal.

67606fd205e98fee67b22293.Description: The 9x19mm Tula Steel Case ammunition is a popular choice for range training. The steel cases are coated with a polymer layer to ensure "reliable" feeding and extraction. Manufactured by Tula.

templates.Description: A 9x19mm Soft Point (SP) ammunition is a popular choice for hunting. The soft point bullet design ensures reliable expansion and penetration.

templates.Name: .300 Blackout TAC-TX
templates.Description: The .300 Blackout TAC-TX ammunition is a popular choice for hunting and defense applications. The TAC-TX has an all-copper design and specially engineered nose cavity. This results in rapid expansion, devastating energy transfer, and weight retention. Manufactured by Barnes.

templates.Name: .300 Blackout TCX
templates.Description: The .300 Blackout TCX (Total Copper X-panding) ammunition is a popular choice for hunting and defense applications. It has consistent penetration that meets or exceeds FBI standards, and expansion that reliably outperforms typical JHP (Jacketed HollowPoint) projectiles. Manufactured by Lehigh Defense.
